
```{=html}

<div class="list grid" style="column-gap: 10px;">
<% for (const item of items) { %>
  <div class="card border-2 rounded-3 g-col-12 g-col-sm-6 g-col-md-4 mb-2" <%= metadataAttrs(item) %> style="margin:10px">
  <div style="margin:30px">
    <img src="<%- item.image %>" alt="<%- item.title %>" width="100%"/>
    <h2><%= item.title %></h2>
    <h3 style="font-style:italic"><%= item.subtitle %></h3>
    <div><%- item.description %></div>
  </div>
  </div>
<% } %>
</div>

```
